<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Rose Wedding Concierge</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/custom.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="logo">
        <h1><img id="logo-img" src="images/roselogohorizontal.png" alt="Rose Wedding Concierge"></h1>
      </div>
      <h2 class="tagline">Rose is a concierge service for your wedding guests.</h2>
      <form class="email-form" action="#" method="post">
        <input type="email" name="email" value="" placeholder="Email..."><!--
        --><input type="submit" class="btn-form" name="" value="Get In Touch">
      </form>
      <div class="header-testimonial">
        "Rose made it easy for us to notify guests about important wedding details, and even acted like a personal assistant for each guest for selecting a hotel, registry gift and more."
        <br>
        <strong>-Kendrick & Alison</strong>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="chat-example">
          <img src="images/rosechat1.png" alt="">
          <img src="images/rosechat3.png" alt="">
          <img src="images/rosechat2.png" alt="">
        </div>
      <div class="feature-description">
        <h2>Your guests have questions. Rose answers them.</h2>
        <p>Rose is a like a personal assistant for your wedding guests. Your family and friends can use Rose to find the information they need about your event, and even get personalized help finding flights, lodging and much more.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-description">
        <h2>Rose reminds your guests about important details.</h2>
        <p>When you use Rose for your wedding, you can make sure your guests are kept up to date with event information, and remind them about important details like the schedule, your registry, RSVP deadlines and more.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-description">
        <h2>Communication is professional and human.</h2>
        <p>Rose is powered by a team of highly skilled and educated humans, so communication with guests is always personalized and professional. Rose gets to know your guests and can assist them with complex tasks, letting guests focus on your big day.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-description">
        <h2>Things your guests can ask Rose.</h2>
        <div class="example">
          <img src="images/gift.svg" alt="">
          <h3>“Rose, could you send me the registry information?”</h3>
          <h4>&rarr; Rose sends link to registry &rarr; Offers to provide gift selection advice</h4>
        </div>

        <div class="example">
          <img src="images/dresscode.svg" alt="">
          <h3>“What’s the dress code? Also, does this outfit look good in your opinion?”</h3>
          <h4>&rarr; Rose sends dress code info &rarr; Gives style advice on proposed outfit</h4>
        </div>

        <div class="example">
          <img src="images/lodging.svg" alt="">
          <h3>“Rose, what hotels do you recommend I look at in the area?”</h3>
          <h4>&rarr; Rose sends hotel recommendations</h4>
        </div>

        <div class="example">
          <img src="images/champagne.svg" alt="">
          <h3>"I don't know too many people at this wedding. Anyone you think I should meet?"</h3>
          <h4>&rarr; Rose asks guest about likes & interests &rarr; Offers to make introductions</h4>
        </div>

        <div class="example">
          <img src="images/flight1.svg" alt="">
          <h3>"Could you help me find a good flight?"</h3>
          <h4>&rarr; Rose asks about desired departure info &rarr; Sends possible flight options</h4>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-description">
        <h2>Things Rose can remind your guests about.</h2>

        <div class="example">
          <img src="images/hotel.svg" alt="">
          <h3>“Steve & Sarah’s wedding is 2 months away! Make sure you book a room. Message me if you need help finding a hotel”</h3>
          <h4>&rarr; You tell Rose to schedule message &rarr; Rose sends text to guests</h4>
        </div>

        <div class="example">
          <img src="images/flowers.svg" alt="">
          <h3>“Wondering what to get the bride and groom? Here’s a link to Brennan and Marta’s registry: link”</h3>
          <h4>&rarr; Rose sends link to registry &rarr; Guests can message Rose for advice</h4>
        </div>

        <div class="example">
          <img src="images/invite.svg" alt="">
          <h3>“Make sure to RSVP by August 10th for Chris and Jacob’s wedding! Message me if you have any questions :)”</h3>
          <h4>&rarr; You tell Rose to contact guests who haven't RSVP'd &rarr; Rose can collect guest status info</h4>
        </div>
      </div>

      <form class="email-form" action="#" method="post">
        <input class="main-form" type="email" name="email" value="" placeholder="Email..."><!--
        --><input type="submit" class="btn-form main-form" name="" value="Get In Touch">
      </form>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <img src="images/rosecake.svg" alt="">
      <h1>Rose</h1>
      <p>Made with &#9829 in North Beach, SF</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
